    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil half a kettle</p><p>Heat a medium-sized pot with a matching lid with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>over a high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>diced chicken thigh</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and cook for 3-4 min or until starting to brown</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
