            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the chicken has browned, reduce the heat to medium-high</p><p>Add the<strong> diced onion </strong>and <strong>chopped potato</strong> to the pot with the <strong>diced carrot</strong> and <strong>chopped garlic </strong>and cook for 3-4 min or until the onion has started to soften</p><p>Season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and a generous grind of<strong> black pepper</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
