    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the onion has softened, add 1 tbsp<span class=\"text-danger\"> [2 tbsp] </span><strong>flour</strong> and cook for a further 1-2 min</p><p>Add the <strong>chicken stock mix </strong>and <strong>soft cheese</strong> to the pot with 200ml<span class=\"text-danger\"> [350ml] </span><strong>boiled water </strong>and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Cook, covered, for 15-20 min or until the potatoes are fork-tender and the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!)</p>",
      "order": 4,
