    {
      "instruction": "<p>Dust your work surface with a generous sprinkling of <strong>flour</strong></p><p>Unwrap the <strong>puff pastry</strong> and roll it out to approx. 0.5cm thickness with a <strong>rolling pin</strong></p><p>Score a 1cm border around the edge of the pastry with a knife, then carefully score inside the border in a criss-cross pattern</p>",
