      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick with a matching lid) with a knob of <strong>butter</strong> over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>scored puff pastry</strong> and cook, covered, for 8-10 min on each side or until the pastry is cooked through, puffed up and golden</p><p>Tip: Cooking for 4? Use 2 pans!</p>",
